CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 8, 1957, pg. A13 reads: "Magic Surrounds Girl Friends' Pittsburgh Meet"
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, from left: saxophone player Nate Harper, unknown man, Walt Harper, Tiny Irvin, bass player Billy Lewis, and unknown man, standing in Webster Hall for Thirtieth Anniversary Convention of Girl Friends, Inc.
